room_title: Escape room "Zombie Autopsy" by Gulf Coast Escape Room in Destin
room_description: You are trapped in a lab that was used to autopsy zombies for the cure for the zombie plague that has taken over the world. Many zombies were autopsied in this room and many parts are left behind. It is your job to find out what happened and how to stop them and escape the room within 60 mins.
